<subSubSection pageId="191" pageNumber="192" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="191.[151,1437,940,1072]" pageId="191" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,940,965]" pageId="191" pageNumber="192">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The new genus clearly differs from the other anthroleucosomatids by the presence of very small body and in the structure of the anterior gonopods which are characterized by the presence of a well-developed sternal processes on anterior side which are fused in the upper ¾, basally divided.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,958,1047,1072]" pageId="191" pageNumber="192" type="etymology">
